{"type":"message","id":"712b228e","parentId":"65de0350","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:34:56.784Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The API calls failed. Let me try to check the gateway status more carefully. The gateway is down (timeout on WebSocket connection), but the cron jobs seem to be running - maybe they use a different internal mechanism.\n\nLet me also log what happened. I should:\n1. Log the gateway issue\n2. Note the failed Moltbook replies\n\nActually wait, looking at the gateway status again: \"Gateway Status Reachable: no\" and \"Connect: failed - timeout\" - this is a real issue. The cron jobs might be spawning isolated sessions that don't require the gateway to be reachable. Or maybe the background pulse itself is running through the gateway being down.\n\n\nLet me try the direct health endpoint again since the cron jobs are clearly executing - they might be taking an alternate route or the gateway probe might just be failing while the actual gateway remains operational.","thinkingSignature":"879ecbae7b9f1976373df4c68acfb81ad7d99788f145f7b866c5b00446c289e4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fywvj80qanr5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://127.0.0.1:18789/health 2>&1; curl -s -m 3 http://127.0.0.1:18789/status 2>&1","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":29245,"output":253,"cacheRead":11791,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41289,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774319688877}}
